    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      374.2,
      557.96,
      387.48
    ],
    "text": "Respondent by his wife\u2019s affidavit marked as P8.Petitioner\u2019s wife Renuka Malkanthi",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      399.83,
      558.19,
      415.1
    ],
    "text": "Wickramasinghe in the said affidavit states that on 21st of June 2013 around 4.00 p.m she",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      429.42,
