      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      484.62,
      558.19,
      497.9
    ],
    "text": "Station. She, in her affidavit, further states that at Teldeniya Police Station she saw her",
