      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      510.23,
      558.12,
      525.5
    ],
    "text": "husband being assaulted by the 1st Respondent. She further states that her husband\u2019s face,",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      539.85,
      558.11,
      553.13
    ],
    "text": "hands and two sides of the body were swollen. This observation suggests that the Petitioner had",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      567.45,
      558.06,
      580.73
    ],
    "text": "sustained injuries in the said areas. But in the petition and affidavit filed by the Petitioner in",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      593.06,
      558.12,
      608.33
    ],
    "text": "this Court , he does not state that the 1st Respondent gave blows to the said areas of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      622.65,
      557.98,
      635.93
    ],
    "text": "body. This discrepancy itself raises certain doubts about the truth of the Petitioner\u2019s story. We",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      650.25,
      556.06,
      663.53
    ],
    "text": "further note that the Petitioner\u2019s wife has not annexed her affidavit to the original petition filed",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      721.79,
      558.34,
      735.07
    ],
    "text": "4",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      92.66,
      56.75,
      558.15,
      70.03
    ],
    "text": "by the Petitioner in this Court. The affidavit filed by the Petitioner's wife marked P8 has been",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      84.37,
      366.43,
      97.65
    ],
    "text": "annexed only with the counter affidavit of the Petitioner.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      92.66,
      137.58,
      558.26,
      152.85
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner also tries to support the assault launched by the 1st Respondent by an",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      167.17,
      558.2,
      180.45
    ],
    "text": "affidavit given by Charuka Iroshana Ratnayake marked P9. According to P9, he was arrested",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      194.77,
      557.92,
      208.05
    ],
    "text": "by Police officers attached to Teldeniya Police Station around 4.30 p.m on 21.06.2013 and was",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      222.37,
      558.06,
      235.65
    ],
    "text": "brought to the Police Station, Teldeniya. We note that the said affidavit has also been marked",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      250.0,
      558.09,
      263.28
    ],
    "text": "only along with the counter affidavit of the Petitioner. The said affidavit has not been annexed",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      277.6,
      557.97,
      290.88
    ],
    "text": "to the original petition and affidavit of the Petitioner. Thus the truth of the material stated",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      305.2,
      221.33,
      318.48
    ],
    "text": "in P8 and P9 is doubtful.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      92.66,
      360.4,
      558.24,
      373.68
    ],
    "text": "After he was arrested he was produced before the Magistrate and he was granted bail on",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      388.02,
      558.04,
      401.3
    ],
    "text": "24.06.2013. Thereafter he got himself admitted to Teldeniya Hospital. He had complained to the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      413.63,
      558.2,
      428.9
    ],
    "text": "Doctor at Teldeniya Hospital that he was assaulted by the 1st Respondent in his genital region,",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      443.22,
      558.13,
      456.5
    ],
    "text": "lower abdomen, neck and right hand. But the Doctor has observed contusion only on left",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      470.82,
      557.88,
      484.1
    ],
    "text": "thigh. Although the Doctor observed a contusion on the left thigh, the Petitioner had not",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      498.42,
      557.98,
      511.7
    ],
    "text": "complained to the Doctor that he was assaulted by the O.I.C in his left thigh. When we consider",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      526.02,
      558.0,
      539.3
    ],
    "text": "the above material, we observe that there is a discrepancy between his complaint to the Doctor",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      553.65,
      294.05,
      566.93
    ],
    "text": "and the observations made by the Doctor.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      34.92,
      608.85,
      557.91,
      622.13
    ],
    "text": "This Court by its order dated 25.08.2014 has granted leave to proceed for alleged",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      86.66,
      636.45,
      558.13,
      649.73
    ],
    "text": "violation of Article 11 of the Constitution. When a person makes an allegation of torture under",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      86.66,
      664.05,
      557.93,
      677.33
    ],
    "text": "Article 11 of the Constitution, a high degree of certainty of his story is required. This view is",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      86.66,
      691.67,
      555.14,
      704.95
    ],
    "text": "supported by the judicial decision in Channa Pieris and others Vs The Attorney-General -",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman",
      "Times New Roman,BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      721.79,
      558.34,
      735.07
    ],
    "text": "5",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      86.66,
      56.75,
      558.34,
      70.03
    ],
    "text": "1994(1) SLR page 01 wherein His Lordship Dr. Justice A.R.B. Amarasinghe held thus:- \u201c",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman",
      "Times New Roman,BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      86.66,
      84.37,
      560.94,
      97.65
    ],
    "text": "Having regard to the nature and gravity of the issue, a high degree of certainty is required,",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      86.66,
      111.97,
      558.14,
      125.25
    ],
    "text": "before the balance of probability might be said to tilt in favour of a Petitioner endeavouring to",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      86.66,
      139.57,
      558.01,
      152.85
    ],
    "text": "discharge his burden of proving that he was subjected to torture or to cruel, inhuman or",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      86.66,
      167.17,
      197.3,
      180.45
    ],
    "text": "degrading treatment.\u201d",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      36.36,
      222.37,
      557.93,
      235.65
    ],
    "text": "We have earlier pointed out that the story narrated by the Petitioner is doubtful. When we",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      85.94,
      250.0,
      557.91,
      263.28
    ],
    "text": "consider all the above matters, we are unable to place high reliance on the story narrated by the",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      85.94,
      277.6,
      558.32,
      290.88
    ],
    "text": "Petitioner. Therefore we hold that the Petitioner has not proved his case with high degree of",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman",
      "Times New Roman,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      85.94,
      305.2,
      558.27,
      318.48
    ],
    "text": "certainty. When we consider all the above matters, we are unable to believe the story narrated by",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      85.94,
      332.8,
      557.89,
      346.08
    ],
    "text": "the Petitioner. For the above reasons, we dismiss the Petitioner\u2019s case. Considering the facts of",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      85.94,
      360.4,
      301.85,
      373.68
    ],
    "text": "this case, we do not make an order for costs.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      388.02,
      307.85,
      401.3
    ],
    "text": "Petition is dismissed.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      56.64,
      443.46,
      503.5,
      456.74
    ],
    "text": "JUDGE OF THE SUPREME COURT",
    "fonts": [
      "Times New Roman",
